do" lang="io" hreflang="io" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ido</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-is"><a href="https://is.wikipedia.org/wiki/Franska_byltingin" title="Franska byltingin — islandais" lang="is" hreflang="is" class="interlanguage-link-target">Íslenska</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-it"><a href="https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rivoluzione_francese" title="Rivoluzione francese — italien" lang="it" hreflang="it" class="interlanguage-link-target">Italiano</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ja"><a href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%95%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD" title="フランス革命 — japonais" lang="ja" hreflang="ja" class="interlanguage-link-target">日本語</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-jam"><a href="https://jam.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_Revaluushan" title="French Revaluushan — créole jamaïcain" lang="jam" hreflang="jam" class="interlanguage-link-target">Patois</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-jv"><a href="https://jv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Revolusi_Prancis" title="Revolusi Prancis — javanais" lang="jv" hreflang="jv" class="interlanguage-link-target">Jawa</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ka"><a href="https://ka.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E1%83%A1%E1%83%90%E1%83%A4%E1%83%A0%E1%83%90%E1%83%9C%E1%83%92%E1%83%94%E1%83%97%E1%83%98%E1%83%A1_%E1%83%A0%E1%83%94%E1%83%95%E1%83%9D%E1%83%9A%E1%83%A3%E1%83%AA%E1%83%98%E1%83%90" title="საფრანგეთის რევოლუცია — géorgien" lang="ka" hreflang="ka" class="interlanguage-link-target">ქართული</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kaa"><a href="https://kaa.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fransuz_ko%27terilisi" title="Fransuz ko&#039;terilisi — karakalpak" lang="kaa" hreflang="kaa" class="interlanguage-link-target">Qaraqalpaqsha</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kbp"><a href="https://kbp.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frans%C9%A9%C9%A9_t%C9%9B_kp%C9%9Bl%C9%A9_l%C9%9Bz%CA%8A%CA%8A" title="Fransɩɩ tɛ kpɛlɩ lɛzʊʊ — Kabiye" lang="kbp" hrefla